{
  "stem": "268.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he-- he would rather take a book or a newspaper or serious books and read.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I would say, let's go outside.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's kick some ball.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then as he would kick, he would kick it kind of awkward, you know, and I would make fun out of him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he could make fun out of me when it came to the [? scholarly. ?] So I would say, gosh, why can't you do like the other brothers?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he was especially gifted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What language did you speak at home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a very interesting question.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's an interesting concept, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We spoke at home Yiddish mixed with Polish sometimes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father was fluent in German, because he worked under the German administration.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I must also say he was pro-German, as far as his political leanings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As soon as I stepped outside the [? trestle ?] and closed the door and I was outside, like, I would go to a different country or another planet.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yiddish was forgotten altogether.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was switched over to Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No sooner the door closed behind me, I was already thinking in Polish, answering in Polish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And if my mom would ever make a mistake and call me for dinner and call me in Yiddish, I wanted to bury my head, you know, in the sand, because why didn't she say it in Polish?",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because the kids would make fun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So to answer your question, the language at home, inside, within our own confinement-- yes, Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Outside, Polish.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And with my neighbors, German sometimes, because these were people who hardly knew Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Poland only took over that territory eight or nine years before my time, so obviously they spoke German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I would speak with them German, as well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But at home, Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
